    <item>
      <title>美国重新实施制裁后，中国减少了对委内瑞拉石油的支付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/china-pays-less-for-venezuelan-oil-after-us-reimposes-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国再次对委内瑞拉石油实施制裁后，中国炼油商购买委内瑞拉石油的价格有所下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/china-pays-less-for-venezuelan-oil-after-us-reimposes-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:22:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LSEG 表示与微软合作将在几个月内发布产品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/lseg-says-microsoft-tie-up-to-release-products-within-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦证券交易所集团表示，由于第一季度盈利符合预期，该公司计划在未来几个月发布与微软公司数据合作伙伴关系产生的一系列产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/lseg-says-microsoft-tie-up-to-release-products-within-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:22:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着日本贸易繁荣，大和的利润增加了一倍多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/daiwa-s-profit-more-than-doubles-as-trading-booms-in-japan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日本基准股指创下历史新高，日本第二大券商的交易量激增，推动大和证券集团的季度利润增长了一倍多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/daiwa-s-profit-more-than-doubles-as-trading-booms-in-japan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:13:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>VinFast 创始人承诺投资 10 亿美元，因电动汽车制造商现金流失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/vinfast-founder-to-give-1-billion-more-for-ev-maker-s-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南亿万富翁 Pham Nhat Vuong 承诺将其个人财富至少再投资 10 亿美元给 VinFast Auto Ltd.，为这家陷入困境的电动汽车制造商提供扩张所需的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/vinfast-founder-to-give-1-billion-more-for-ev-maker-s-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 03:08:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着摩根大通日期临近，印度在廉价债券方面脱颖而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/india-stands-out-for-cheap-bonds-as-jpmorgan-index-date-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股市已飙升成为全球最昂贵的股票之一，但其债券尽管是今年亚洲表现最好的股票，但似乎相对便宜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/india-stands-out-for-cheap-bonds-as-jpmorgan-index-date-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国公布卖空监控系统的细节，以发现非法交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/south-korea-unveils-details-of-short-selling-monitoring-platform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国正在开发一个监控卖空的平台，该平台可以帮助识别非法交易，但该平台似乎不太可能在该国的交易禁令于 6 月到期之前投入使用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/south-korea-unveils-details-of-short-selling-monitoring-platform</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 00:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲通胀最敏感央行的债券面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/bonds-at-risk-from-asia-s-most-inflation-sensitive-central-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通胀担忧和比索疲软，菲律宾央行希望推迟货币宽松政策，亚洲新兴市场表现最差的主权债券面临进一步下跌的风险。]]></description>
